   Purpose     : Standard list/collection page template. Composes PageTemplateV2
                 and provides named slots for title, top-action buttons, filter
                 area, and main table content. Intended as the base for all
                 module list pages (e.g. Students, Staff, Classes).
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Changes     :
     - 1.0.0  2026-03-21  Initial implementation.
     - 1.1.0  2026-03-23  Added BaseLayoutV2 layout binding (Step 2).
     - 1.2.0  2026-03-23  Updated layout directive to fully-qualified
                          BaseLayoutV2 namespace.
     - 1.3.0  2026-03-23  Replaced invalid BodyContent slot with BodyContent
                          to match PageTemplateV2 contract.
